https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500null California's Eastern High Sierra is a region of fun and adventure. This DVD is a great way to share your Highway 395 experience as it explores the spectacular places and activities that make this region one of America's favorite vacation playgrounds. From Bodie Ghost Town to Mammoth Lakes and even the top of Mt. Whitney, this is a fun overview of the Eastern High Sierra. California's Eastern High Sierra
